* Audience Choice: ''Cas'': Pepijn and Sjors' steady, seven-year relationship is shaken up after they allow a young student named Cas to sleep on their couch until he finds a place of his own.<ref>{{Citation|title=Cas (TV Movie 2016)|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt5858380/plotsummary|accessdate=2018-06-11}}</ref>

